# csg
C site generator
This program runs my website at hasanzahra.xyz

run bin/csg with "src" and "dest" command line arguments.

index/metadata            - contains site name
articles/xyz/metadata     - contains metadata for an article
articles/xyz/xyz.html     - contains article contents
style/article.css         - style applied to articles
style/global.css          - global style

make sure dest/ has an "articles" directory. 
copy all other files to dest manually.
